title Stift Plazieren


actor User
participant Screen
participant SoundSystem

loop x4
User->Screen: click_on_hole()
Screen->>SoundSystem: play_tone(click)
Screen-->User:show_color_menu()

User->Screen: select_color(color)
Screen->>SoundSystem: play_tone(click)
Screen->Screen: save_color_temp(color, position)

note right of Screen:color and position are temporarily saved in an array
Screen-->User: show_view()
end
